name: Nintytwo
overview:
Nintytwo is a secure website where registered users can upload their video resumes.

Video resume provides a chance to a user to TALK about their achievements. The users can let his/ her potential employers to access the video resume and view it. The video resume will not available for general access by the public. The users can delete or block a video resume at any time. A user can have only one video resume hosted at Nintytwo.com at a time.

Professionals from any field such as CFO, Programmers, Models, Cooks, Actors are invited to get registered at Nintytwo.com and start using this free service.
